  "description": "Stripe adapter for @paykit/core — instant destination charges with per-component application fees, escrow (manual-capture → capture → release transfer), tips, refunds, setup intents, tiered Billing subscriptions and a typed webhook dispatcher. Structural typing: takes YOUR configured stripe client (any v10+).",
